{"tid":2025153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍拒評李漢民元朗單位及劉肇邦西貢村屋被指有僭建個案","createTime":"2020-05-20T05:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8bdf3e274b6a4232d031d5ca96d72558c1f9f2","tid":2025153,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"警方拒評李漢民元朗單位劉肇邦西貢村屋被指有僭建個案<br />\n2020-05-20 HKT 12:25<br />\n<br />\n有報道指警務處八鄉分區指揮官李漢民名下位於元朗的單位，有3個玻璃屋構建物懷疑屬於僭建，另外，警察公共關係科警司劉肇邦名下位於西貢的村屋，有天台屋懷疑有僭建物。警方表示，不評論個別個案。<br />\n<br />\n本台分別就兩項報道向警方查詢，警方說，傳媒如有相關資料或證據，可向有關部門查詢或投訴，相關人員會積極配合有關部門的調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527228-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527228-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=122355fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527228-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=891bf136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527228-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5665b3638450f4ebf41f7e2ef29546468c74ceb0","tid":2025153,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"點會評論呀 你唔知啲狗屋屋頂都有咩"},{"pid":"1a941f8228de18fbab9fc402cec6bbb1265400e4","tid":2025153,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"做狗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4244269dc3f731c750bccb811b482d01eb438d","tid":2025153,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a941f8228de18fbab9fc402cec6bbb1265400e4","tid":2025153,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"做狗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20